<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-21 01:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4958 &Cx1f; kan-z
r v BC-BC-KAN-BUDGET-KAN &LR;      08-21 0188
