<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-AIR-SAFETY-REVIEW-655&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A BACK-DOOR VIEW OF AIRLINE SAFETY 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For use by special arrangement
