<P>
   ELDERLY-COUPLE (Los Angeles) _ A judge says it is official, and
now the 94-year-old groom may kiss the 86-year-old bride after
fighting the court for the past two years. By Donna Huffaker. (Will
move in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California news files.)
