u v BC-SPOT-SPORTS-BJT-COX     08-21 0631
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT-SPORTS-BJT-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE SUNDAY SPORTS BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These sports stories for release on Sunday, August 22, 1999, are
moving today to clients of the New York Times News Service.
</P>
<P>
