<DOCNO> NYT19990821.0239 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-21 23:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5490 &Cx1f; kan-z
r s BC-NYTROYAL-KAN &LR;      08-21 0578
